strings:
<voice_0x0100172E><se_low>Yangus: Eh!? Wot's goin' on, guv!?
Where's the Princess!?
Wot's 'appened to the weddin'!?

<voice_0x0100172F><se_def>Angelo: Hey, <hero>! Get over here!
We've got trouble!
<voice_0x01001730><se_def>Angelo: King Trode and Princess Medea are surrounded by soldiers down there!
<voice_0x01001731><se_low>Yangus: You wot!? I don't get it!

<voice_0x01001732><se_low>Yangus: But we'd better get a move on, guv!
It don't look good!
<voice_0x01001734><se_def>*: Do you think we'll just let you go after you ruined the royal wedding like that!?
<voice_0x01001735><se_def>Angelo: Leave them to us, <hero>. You just get the Princess and King Trode to safety.
<voice_0x01001736><se_high>Red: Awright then, one last punch-up for the road, eh?
